FOLLOWMYHEALTH
Atlanta Women’s Specialists helps you to manage your Ob/Gyn healthcare securely and online with FollowMyHealth. Easily request a refill, see lab results, contact your doctor and more. 

IN-OFFICE SERVICES
Atlanta Women’s Specialists now offers several procedures in our offices that were formerly available only at hospitals, saving you time, money and the risks of general anesthesia. 

AWS adopts New Pap Smear Guidelines
Atlanta Women’s Specialists has adopted the new guidelines for cervical cancer screening established by the American College of Obstetricians and Gynecologists (ACOG).  




