Better Connection, Better Care
An Atlanta Ob/Gyn that empowers patients.
Does collaboration between doctor and patient lead to better healthcare? Atlanta Women's Specialists thinks so. It's how we approach patient care.
We're using innovative technology to enhance and transform the way we serve you. We're also connecting you to the best health resources. Each of our doctors is proud to be affiliated with Northside Hospital giving you access to the Most Preferred Hospital in Atlanta. On our site you can manage your health and find the most accurate Ob/Gyn information.
The result, we hope, is an informed, empowered and satisfied patient. Learn more.
JUST IN:  Our very own Dr. Michael A. Dawson voted Best OB-GYN in Atlanta.







