OUR SERVICES
Hackensack Meridian Health provides health care services where you and your family need it the most. In the hospital, community, and in-home settings, our services are tailored to your needs, and we are committed to advancing our medical services through clinical education and research. Our comprehensive services include cutting-edge diagnostic procedures, innovative treatment options, and compassionate care by our team of skilled health professionals. 

KEY CLINICAL SERVICES
 






Assisted Living
From the moment you walk through our doors, expect a level of warmth and comfort second only to home, sweet home.
LEARN MORE

Behavioral Health
Meridian has provided comprehensive mental health and substance abuse services to our communities for more than 40 years.

LEARN MORE



Cancer Care
Meridian Cancer Care provides world-class clinical expertise and technology, close to home.
LEARN MORE

Cardiology
Trust Meridian CardioVascular Network for the most complete, coordinated heart and vascular care in the region.
LEARN MORE



Clinical Trials
Meridian experts are leading the way in health care innovation through cutting-edge research and clinical trials.
LEARN MORE

Convenient Care
Get connected to our network of primary care physicians, after hours and urgent care facilities, and range of specialty services. 
LEARN MORE







Fitness Centers
Meridian Fitness and Wellness offers locations and memberships to suit all shapes, sizes and schedules. 
LEARN MORE

Home Care
Meridian Health’s home care services provide unmatched care, services and support through every stage of recovery.
LEARN MORE



Integrative Medicine
Integrative medicine goes beyond treating patients’ immediate symptoms to address the complete range of physical, emotional, mental, social, spiritual and environmental influences that impact daily health.
LEARN MORE

Long-Term Care
Our skilled nursing facilities provide personalized programs to meet the unique needs of every patient and family.  
LEARN MORE



Maternity
Trust our family of experts to be there for your growing family throughout every stage of life – and it all starts here.
LEARN MORE

Meridian Medical Group
Life is a journey. From the birth of a child to routine examinations to managing a chronic condition, our primary care physicians and specialists have got you and your family covered every step of the way. 
LEARN MORE







Neuroscience
Life can change in an instant, which is why we offer the region’s most comprehensive treatment for spine injuries, stroke and more.
LEARN MORE

Orthopedics
Meridian Orthopedics experts are dedicated to helping every patient maintain long term pain-free movement and joint health.
LEARN MORE



Palliative Care
Palliative care is a specific type of care focusing on making patients as comfortable as possible and preventing/relieving suffering. Our palliative services include relief from physical symptoms, support coping with emotional pain and stress, assistance with insurance, and providing support group information.

LEARN MORE

Pediatrics
Trust Meridian's network of pediatric surgeons and specialists for personalized care and attention little ones can count on.
LEARN MORE



Rehabilitation
Meridian Rehabilitation offers a seamless continuum of high quality acute, subacute, outpatient, and home centered care. 
LEARN MORE

Robotic Surgery
Robotic surgery is a breakthrough treatment for a wide variety of conditions that previously required open surgery. 
LEARN MORE







Sleep Medicine
Rest easy knowing our physicians and technologists are trained to diagnosis and treat every type of sleep disorder.
LEARN MORE

Weight-Loss Surgery
Weight-loss procedures through Meridian Health include evaluation, education and support before and after surgery.
LEARN MORE


